SUMMARY:18+ Figure Drawing: June Session
LOCATION:Unkindness Art\, 2923 North Avenue\, Richmond\, VA 23222
DESCRIPTION:Ongoing nude figure drawing series open to all artists 18+. Short pose session with a single model. Tickets required\, no door sales. Must show valid photo ID.\\n\\nCost: $10\\n\\nRegister: https://www.unkindnessart.com/events/nude-figure-drawing-may-2026-4r4rp
URL:https://www.unkindnessart.com/events/nude-figure-drawing-may-2026-4r4rp
