DTEND:20260625T203000
SUMMARY:Figure Drawing Open Studio
LOCATION:Hanover Arts & Activities Center\, 500 South Center Street\, Ashland\, VA 23005
DESCRIPTION:Figure drawing open studio with a live model in a relaxed\, supportive environment. Bring your own drawing materials—tables and chairs provided. Ages 18+.\\n\\nCost: $10\\n\\nRegister: https://www.hanoverarts.net/events/figure-drawing-open-studio
URL:https://www.hanoverarts.net/events/figure-drawing-open-studio
