BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:2026-07-13-1000-manchester-studios-rva@rvafiguredrawing
DTSTAMP:20260621T121838Z
DTSTART:20260713T100000
DTEND:20260713T173000
SUMMARY:The Alchemy Of Expression - Portrait Sculpture Workshop
LOCATION:Manchester Studios RVA\, 1300 West Main Street\, Richmond\, Virginia 23220
DESCRIPTION:Two-week portrait sculpture workshop (July 13-17 and July 20-24\, 2026). Classical Realism methods working from a live model. Covers skull\, muscles\, anatomy\, facial fat pads\, and likeness development. Hours: 10am-1pm and 2:30-5:30pm daily. All materials and model fees included. All skill levels welcome. Register via Zelle to ConstanceBowden@yahoo.com.\\n\\nCost: $1600\\n\\nRegister: https://manchesterstudiosrva.com/upcoming-workshops/
URL:https://manchesterstudiosrva.com/upcoming-workshops/
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:2026-07-29-1945-unkindness-art@rvafiguredrawing
DTSTAMP:20260621T121838Z
DTSTART:20260729T194500
DTEND:20260729T220000
SUMMARY:Drawn to Life: A Crash Course on Life Drawing
LOCATION:Unkindness Art\, 2923 North Avenue\, Richmond\, VA 23222
DESCRIPTION:All-ages crash course on life drawing. Presentation on drawing from life followed by a guided figure drawing session with a live clothed model. Hosted by resident tattoo artist Liam Williams.\\n\\nCost: $10\\n\\nRegister: https://www.unkindnessart.com/events/drawn-to-life
URL:https://www.unkindnessart.com/events/drawn-to-life
END:VEVENT
